Package seng202.team4.model

Class Airport

  • java.lang.Object
    • seng202.team4.model.DataType
      • seng202.team4.model.Airport
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Validate
    public class Airport
extends DataType
    Airport model class with attributes representing the aspects of airports. These attributes were chosen from the open flights sample data. Objects of this class are created to display in the table on the Airport tab.
